    <h2>About us</h2>
    <p>Welcome to the Pokémon News Agency, your premier source for all things Pokémon-related! Established as an extension of the renowned Pokémon Radio network headquartered in Goldenrod City, our agency has been dedicated to delivering timely and accurate news coverage from across the Pokémon world.
